# Web3Forms access key — powers the /contact form's real email delivery.
# Create a free key at https://web3forms.com (no account or backend required):
# enter the inbox address you want enquiries delivered to and copy the key here.
# This value is exposed to the browser (NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix) by design — the
# Web3Forms submit API is called from the client. The key only authorises
# delivery to your configured inbox; it grants no other access.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
